TITLE      2H induced reactions on 8Li and primordial NUCLEO-
            synthesis
FACILITY   (VDGT,1USANOT) 80 MV Van de Graaff accelerator
INC-SOURCE 8Li ions from Notre Dame-Michigan-Ohio state
            radioactive beam facility with energies 8.0 -14.0 MeV.
SAMPLE     Deuterated Polyethylene (CD2) with a thickness of
            830 microg/cm**2.
DETECTOR   (TELES) Two delta E-E solid state detector telescopes.
METHOD     (EDE)
            Deuteron spectra obtained using subtraction procedure
            for Polyethylene (CD2) minus carbon spectra.
